des:
AM 600 KSJB offers listeners Local News, AG News, Weather, Your Favorite Personalities & the best in Classic Country Music 24 hrs. a day. To enable the skill, say "Alexa, enable k. s. j. b. skill."

KSJB has been around since the early days of Radio. In March of 2012 celebrated their 75th Anniversary. KSJB offers listeners Local News, Local Sports and Local Weather along with AG News from the Red River Farm Network and all of your favorite Classic County Hits.
